---
title: Garlic Herb Butter–Basted Scallops with Spaghetti & Burst Grape Tomatoes
description: Searing tender scallops in herby browned butter is just one of the ways you’ll elevate this impressive pasta bowl. Juicy burst grape tomatoes add sunny verve to spaghetti in a rich, garlicky cream sauce. You’ll finish it all with a squeeze of lemon, then sprinkle with umami-rich Parmesan cheese and fresh, verdant parsley just before serving for a meal that flawlessly balances rich and fresh flavors.
